track_notes: To reach the starting point you need a to drive the car on a forest road (not for a Ferrari). The walk is very nice. You can activate some summits next door too, if you are healthy.

You must have a car that can go on forest road to reach the parking. Then it is very nice place to walk, to reach the summit there is no path, you must climb as a goat! the descent is easier to the east but you need to be a bit feet solid!
